import {NavLink, Outlet} from 'react-router-dom';

import Subnavigation from '../layouts/subnavigation'
import SubnavItem from '../layouts/subnavitem'

import styled from 'styled-components'
import '../styles/theme.css'

const Explore = () => (
  <StyledContainer>
    <Subnavigation title='Explore'>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/explore/spans'>Spans</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/explore/errors'>Errors</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/explore/replays'>Replays</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
      <SubnavItem>
        <NavLink to='/explore/logs'>Logs</NavLink>
      </SubnavItem>
    </Subnavigation>
    <Outlet/>
  </StyledContainer>
);

const StyledContainer = styled('div')`
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 200px auto;
`;

export default Explore;
